{"word":"G4098 - πίπτω - píptō - pip'-to - Fail","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πίπτω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">píptō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pip'-to</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Fail</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - விழு"},{"paragraph":"to fall"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>The first is a reduplicated and contracted form of the second (which occurs only as an alternate in certain tenses); probably akin to <a href=\"#/G4072 - πέτομαι - pétomai - pet'-om-ahee/4072\">G4072</a> through the idea of <i>alighting</i>; to <i>fall</i> (literally of figuratively): - fail, fall (down), light on.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1601/1601\">G1601</a>, <a href=\"#/G2667/2667\">G2667</a>, <a href=\"#/G3895/3895\">G3895</a>, <a href=\"#/G3900/3900\">G3900</a>, <a href=\"#/G4045/4045\">G4045</a>, <a href=\"#/G4098/4098\">G4098</a>, <a href=\"#/G4430/4430\">G4430</a>, <a href=\"#/G4431/4431\">G4431</a>"}]}